description.en: We are a deflationary token on the bsc network who recently launched a full scale fantasy sports platform with crypto integration. Our focus is merging the worlds of fantasy sports and crypto while bringing a unique and innovative experience to the space. Planned utilities also include our NFT marketplace, metaverse implementations, staking, and more.
